cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing dialogue agents that can imitate the personalities of fictional characters through language modeling. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a method for learning dialogue agents that exhibit human-like characteristics. 
- cs.LG (Learning) is relevant as the paper introduces a three-component system for building character-specific language models. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) may be relevant as the paper discusses the development of a dataset and system for dialogue agents. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) may be relevant as the paper involves language style retrieval for specific characters.
